"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34101,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/06\/allah-loves-concessions\/","url_meta":{"origin":33423,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Rukhsa: Allah loves believers taking His concessions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah loves for you to take His concessions, just as He loves you to fulfill His edicts.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 354 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15483,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/29\/dua-prophet-travelers\/","url_meta":{"origin":33423,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet supplicates for travelers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I intend to travel, so instruct me.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou must be mindful of Allah and exalt Him every time you ascend a height.\u201d As the man turned to leave, the Prophet said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39882,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/22\/shahada-absolves-idolatry\/","url_meta":{"origin":33423,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Shirk: Word of faith absolves from idolatry","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 22, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Salam reported: We were travelling with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, when people were heard saying, \u201cWhich deeds are best, O Messenger of Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cFaith in Allah and His Messenger, jihad in the way of Allah, and a righteous Hajj\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25163,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/08\/14\/waswas-angels-devils\/","url_meta":{"origin":33423,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Waswas: Angels suggest good, devils suggest evil","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 14, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Satan influences the son of Adam and so does the angel. As for the influence of Satan, he threatens evil and denies the truth. As for the influence of the angel, he promises goodness\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/cat